  "lesson": {
    "title": "Astable Multivibrator (Variable Rate)",
    "description": "Variable-rate astable multivibrator. Two NPN stages are cross-coupled by 10uF capacitors and drive mirrored 470 ohm plus LED collector loads. A potentiometer in the timing network changes the blink rate while fixed resistors keep the oscillator stable."
